replies.body:
Came back to League after like a 8 month hiatus. First match? Let's play my old main! {{champion:34}} 

0-8 by 20 minutes
Entire team was more or less being passive aggressive towards me, not flaming me or anything but it was clear they were mad. Couldn't blame them, really. I knew I was playing like trash. Didn't make me feel better though.

Didn't play Anivia for like a year ;.;
